<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11688</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17519</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡拉巴斯在镇上买面粉和盐。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17519</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23342</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>商人等着卡拉巴斯数硬币。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23342</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28616</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>桌子上有一篮鱼干。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28616</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33260</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡拉巴斯看到鱼干，想起了普斯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33260</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36821</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“鱼干多少钱？” 他问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36821</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41360</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>商人告诉了他价钱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41360</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47500</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太贵了。” 卡拉巴斯想，“算了吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47500</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55974</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他付了面粉和盐的钱就离开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55974</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60703</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡拉巴斯在回家的路上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60703</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63867</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，他停了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63867</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68453</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“普斯是一只很好的猫。” 卡拉巴斯想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68453</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72680</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想为他做点什么。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72680</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76321</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡拉巴斯跑了回去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76321</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85308</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他买了一片鱼干。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85308</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91610</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡拉巴斯走了很长的路回家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91610</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101430</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的一只鞋破了。但是他笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101430</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108290</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他想快点把小礼物送给普斯！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108290</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114061</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>普斯吃完了鱼干。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114061</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119733</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他发出开心的叫声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119733</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126864</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你喜欢，我也很开心。” 卡拉巴斯说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126864</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133215</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>晚餐后，卡拉巴斯又数了数硬币。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133215</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136410</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每天硬币都在变少。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136410</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我该怎么办？” 他说，“我要怎么吃饭呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146382</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>普斯跳到主人的腿上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146382</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149824</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡拉巴斯叹了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149824</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154854</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你真幸运，普斯。你没有烦恼。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154854</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159425</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不是的，主人。” 普斯突然说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159425</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的烦恼就是我的烦恼。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165932</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡拉巴斯吓了一跳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165932</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176456</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你……你会说话！”</Text>
